'''重大{{zy|創|chuāng|ㄔㄨㄤ}}傷'''（{{lang-en|Major trauma}}）是指任何可能導致長期[[失能|失能]]或[[死亡|死亡]]的[[創傷|創傷]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Glossary|url=http://www.nhtsa.gov/people/injury/ems/emstraumasystem03/glossary.htm|work=National Highway Traffic Safety Administration|accessdate=26 March 2014|archive-date=2016-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127050953/http://www.nhtsa.gov/people/injury/ems/emstraumasystem03/glossary.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。造成重大創傷的原因很多，包含{{le|鈍性創傷|Blunt trauma}}和{{le|穿透性創傷|Penetrating trauma}}，例如[[跌倒|跌倒]]、[[車禍|車禍]]、{{le|刺傷|Stab wound}}、{{le|槍傷|Gunshot wound}}。

2002年，[[意外事故|意外事故]]和故意傷害是全球第五和第七大死因，分別佔所有死亡人數的6.23%和2.84%。基於研究目的，重大創傷定義為{{le|外傷嚴重度分數|Injury Severity Score}}<ref name=CMU>{{cite web |title=外傷嚴重度分數 |url=http://www2.cmu.edu.tw/~cmcmd/ctanatomy/clinical/styled-6/ISSscore-1.html |website=中國醫藥大學醫學影像學習園地 |accessdate=2020-09-12 |archive-date=2019-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909182103/http://www2.cmu.edu.tw/~cmcmd/ctanatomy/clinical/styled-6/ISSscore-1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=外傷嚴重度分數（ISS） |url=https://www.nhi.gov.tw/Resource/webdata/29801_1_ISS%E5%A4%96%E5%82%B7%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%BA%A6%E5%88%86%E6%95%B8%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC1050204.pdf |website=衛生福利部中央健康保險署 |accessdate=2020-09-23}}</ref>大於15<ref>{{cite journal|last=Palmer|first=C|title=Major trauma and the injury severity score—where should we set the bar?|journal=Annual Proceedings of the Association for the Advancement of Automotive Medicine |year=2007|volume=51|pages=13–29|pmid=18184482|pmc=3217501}}</ref>。

== 分類 ==
創傷通常按嚴重程度、傷害的位置、或綜合兩者來進行分類<ref>Moore 2013, p. 77</ref>。創傷也可以按[[人口統計學|人口統計學]]分類，例如年齡或性別<ref name="Rosen2010">{{cite book|title=Rosen's emergency medicine: concepts and clinical practice|url=https://archive.org/details/rosensemergencym00mdjo|edition= 7th |last=Marx|first=J|year=2010|publisher=Mosby/Elsevier|location=Philadelphia|isbn=978-0323054720|pages=[https://archive.org/details/rosensemergencym00mdjo/page/n266 243]–842}}</ref>。也可以根據傷害對身體施力的類型進行分類，例如鈍性創傷或穿透性創傷。出於研究目的，可以使用基於[[國際疾病與相關健康問題統計分類|國際疾病與相關健康問題統計分類]]（ICD-9-CM）的巴雷爾氏診斷統計矩陣（{{lang|en|Barel matrix}}）對創傷進行分類，用於將創傷分類{{le|International standard||國際標準化}}<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/injury/ice/barell_matrix.htm|title = The Barell Injury Diagnosis Matrix, Classification by Body Region and Nature of the Injury|accessdate = 19 June 2013|publisher = Center for Disease Control|archive-date = 2019-10-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191015120514/https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/injury/ice/barell_matrix.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>。重大創傷有時按身體部位分類，其中40%是多重創傷，30%頭部損傷，20%胸部創傷，10%腹部創傷，2%肢體創傷<ref name="Rosen2010"/><ref name="ER2008">{{cite journal|last1=Bonatti|first1=H|last2=Calland|first2=JF|title=Trauma|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_emergency-medicine-clinics-of-north-america_2008-08_26_3/page/625|journal=Emergency Medicine Clinics of North America|volume=26|issue=3|pages=625–48|year=2008|pmid=18655938|doi=10.1016/j.emc.2008.05.001}}</ref>。

有多種量表可量化評估損傷的嚴重程度，用於對病患進行分類或統計分析。{{le|簡易外傷分數|Abbreviated Injury Scale}}<ref>{{cite web|title=外傷嚴重度分數|url=http://www2.cmu.edu.tw/~cmcmd/ctanatomy/clinical/styled-6/ISSscore-1.html|accessdate=2020-09-11|website=中國醫藥大學醫學影像學習園地|archive-date=2019-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909182103/http://www2.cmu.edu.tw/~cmcmd/ctanatomy/clinical/styled-6/ISSscore-1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[昏迷指數|格拉斯哥昏迷指數]]常用於量化損傷程度以進行分類，並可讓醫療系統在臨床環境中監視或預測病患的病情趨勢<ref>Moore 2013, pp. 77–98</ref>。數據也可用於[[流行病學|流行病學]]調查和研究<ref>{{cite conference|url=https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/injury/DicussionDocu.pdf|title=Discussion document on injury severity measurement in administrative datasets|publisher=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|accessdate=2013-05-24|date=September 2004|pages=1–3|archive-date=2017-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829050443/https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/injury/DicussionDocu.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

嚴重創傷的病患中約有2%患有[[脊髓損傷|脊髓損傷]]<ref name="Ahn 1341–61">{{cite journal|last=Ahn|first=H|author2=Singh, J |author3=Nathens, A |author4=MacDonald, RD |author5=Travers, A |author6=Tallon, J |author7=Fehlings, MG |author8= Yee, A |title=Pre-hospital care management of a potential spinal cord injured patient: a systematic review of the literature and evidence-based guidelines|journal=Journal of Neurotrauma|date=Aug 2011|volume=28|issue=8|pages=1341–61|pmid=20175667 |doi=10.1089/neu.2009.1168 |pmc=3143405}}</ref>。

== 病因 ==
任何作用於身體的物理性外力都可能造成損傷<ref>Moore 2013, p. 2</ref>。創傷致死的主要原因是鈍性創傷、車禍、跌倒，其次是刺傷等穿透性創傷<ref name="EMT-BMcGraw">{{cite book|title=EMT-Basic|url=https://archive.org/details/mcgrawhillsemtba0000dipr|last=DiPrima Jr.|first=PA|pages=[https://archive.org/details/mcgrawhillsemtba0000dipr/page/227 227]–33|publisher=McGraw-Hill|isbn=978-0071496797|date=2008-03-21}}</ref><ref name="ec11">{{cite book|title=Emergency Care|vauthors=Dickenson ET, Limmer D, O'Keefe MF |isbn=978-0135005231|year=2009}}</ref>。

作為統計用途，傷害分為故意傷害（例如自殺）或[[意外事故|意外事故]]（例如車禍）。故意傷害是造成創傷的常見原因<ref name="isbn0-340-92826-3">{{cite book |author1=Jeff Garner |author2=Greaves, Ian |author3=Ryan, James R. |author4=Porter, Keith R. |title=Trauma care manual |publisher=Hodder Arnold |location=London |year=2009 |pages= |isbn=978-0340928264 |oclc= |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref>。子彈或刀等{{le|異物|Foreign body}}進入[[組織_(生物學)|人體組織]]可造成開放性傷口，屬於{{le|穿透性創傷|Penetrating trauma}}。在美國，大多數由穿透性創傷造成的死亡發生在都會區，其中80%是由槍支造成的<ref name="isbn078173200x">{{cite book|vauthors=Medzon R, Mitchell EJ |title=Introduction to Emergency Medicine|url=https://archive.org/details/introductiontoem0000unse |publisher=Lippincott Williams & Willkins|location=Philadelphia|year=2005|pages=[https://archive.org/details/introductiontoem0000unse/page/393 393]–431|isbn=978-0781732000}}</ref>。{{le|爆炸傷|Blast injury}}是造成創傷的複合性病因，因為它通常既包括鈍性創傷也包括穿透性創傷，還可能伴有[[灼傷|灼傷]]。創傷也可能與特定活動有關，例如[[職業傷害|職業傷害]]或[[運動傷害|運動傷害]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Kannus|first1=P.|last2=Parkkari|first2=J.|last3=Jarvinen|first3=T.|last4=Jarvinen|first4=A.|last5=Jarvinen|first5=M.|title=Basic science and clinical studies coincide: active treatment approach is needed after a sports injury|journal=Scandinavian Journal of Medicine & Science in Sports|date=June 2003|volume=13|issue=3|pages=150–54|doi=10.1034/j.1600-0838.2003.02225.x|pmid=12753486}}</ref>。

