=== 理學檢查 ===
第一階段[[理學檢查|理學檢查]]要確認任何危及生命的問題，可能在運送病患的過程中或到達醫院時執行。第二階段理學檢查包括對[[腹部|腹部]]、[[骨盆|骨盆]]、[[胸部|胸部]]區域的系統評估、完整檢視身體表面以發現所有損傷、以及{{le|神經學檢查|Neurological examination}}。損傷的徵象可能稍晚才會顯現，或損傷可能在初步評估中遺漏，例如病患初進醫院[[急診室|急診室]]時<ref name="ATLS2008">{{cite book|first=American College of Surgeons|last=Committee on Trauma|title=ATLS: Advanced Trauma Life Support Program for Doctors|publisher=American College of Surgeons|location=Chicago|edition=8th|year=2008|isbn=978-1880696316}}</ref>。通常理學檢查是有系統地進行，首先檢查是否存在任何即時生命威脅（初步調查），然後進行更深入的檢查（二次調查）<ref>Moore 2013, p</ref>。

=== 影像檢查 ===
[[File:Whole_body_radiograph_in_trauma.jpg|thumb]][[骨折|骨折]]，屬於重大創傷。]]
重大創傷病患通常會接受胸部和骨盆的[[醫學影像#X射線|X光檢查]]<ref name="ER2008" />，並根據損傷的機轉和表現使用{{le|外傷重點式超音波評估|Focused assessment with sonography for trauma}}（{{lang|en|FAST}}）檢查是否有{{le|內部出血|Internal bleeding}}。對於[[血壓|血壓]]和[[心率|心率]]相對穩定且[[血氧濃度|血氧濃度]]較高的病患，[[電腦斷層掃描|電腦斷層掃描]]很有用<ref name="ER2008" /><ref name="Trauma2010" />。{{le|全身電腦斷層掃描|Full-body CT scan}}可以提高重大創傷病患的[[存活率|存活率]]<ref name="Huber2009">{{cite journal |vauthors=Huber-Wagner S, Lefering R, Qvick LM, etal |title=Effect of whole-body CT during trauma resuscitation on survival: a retrospective, multicentre study|journal=Lancet|volume=373|issue=9673|pages=1455–61|year=2009|pmid=19321199|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(09)60232-4}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Jiang|first1=L|last2=Ma|first2=Y|last3=Jiang|first3=S|last4=Ye|first4=L|last5=Zheng|first5=Z|last6=Xu|first6=Y|last7=Zhang|first7=M|title=Comparison of whole-body computed tomography vs selective radiological imaging on outcomes in major trauma patients: a meta-analysis|journal=Scandinavian Journal of Trauma, Resuscitation and Emergency Medicine|date=September 2, 2014|volume=22|issue=1|page=54|pmid=25178942|doi=10.1186/s13049-014-0054-2|pmc=4347587}}</ref>。這些掃描使用靜脈注射的[[造影劑|造影劑]]，而非口服的<ref name="Allen2004">{{cite journal|vauthors=Allen TL, Mueller MT, Bonk RT, Harker CP, Duffy OH, Stevens MH |title=Computed tomographic scanning without oral contrast solution for blunt bowel and mesenteric injuries in abdominal trauma|journal=J Trauma|volume=56|issue=2|pages=314–22|year=2004|pmid=14960973|doi=10.1097/01.TA.0000058118.86614.51}}</ref>。有專家擔心在創傷不明的狀況下，未先確認腎功能是否足夠就給予靜脈造影劑，也許會損害腎臟，但相關證據並未發現顯著損害<ref name="Trauma2010">{{cite journal |vauthors=McGillicuddy EA, Schuster KM, Kaplan LJ, et al |title=Contrast-induced nephropathy in elderly trauma patients|journal=J Trauma|volume=68|issue=2|pages=294–97|year=2010|pmid=20154540|doi=10.1097/TA.0b013e3181cf7e40}}</ref>。

在[[美國|美國]]，[[急診室|急診室]]有15%的創傷病患接受電腦斷層掃描或[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振檢查]]<ref name="Korley2010">{{cite journal|vauthors=Korley FK, Pham JC, Kirsch TD |title=Use of advanced radiology during visits to US emergency departments for injury-related conditions,1998–2007| journal=JAMA| volume=304| issue=13| pages=1465–71| year=2010| pmid=20924012| doi=10.1001/jama.2010.1408}}</ref>。[[低血壓|低血壓]]或心率加快且懷疑腹部出血時，建議跳過電腦斷層掃描而直接進行手術<ref>{{cite journal  |vauthors=Neal MD, Peitzman AB, Forsythe RM, etal |title=Over reliance on computed tomography imaging in patients with severe abdominal injury: is the delay worth the risk? |journal=J Trauma |volume=70 |issue=2 |pages=278–84 |date=February 2011 |pmid=21307722 |doi=10.1097/TA.0b013e31820930f9 |url=}}</ref>。現代的64切電腦斷層掃描可以高度準確地排除鈍性創傷是否造成重要的[[頸部|頸部]]損傷<ref>{{cite journal|last=Kanji|first=HD|author2=Neitzel, A |author3=Sekhon, M |author4=McCallum, J |author5= Griesdale, DE |title=Sixty-four-slice computed tomographic scanner to clear traumatic cervical spine injury: systematic review of the literature.|journal=Journal of Critical Care|date=Apr 2014|volume=29|issue=2|pages=314.e9–13|pmid=24393410 |doi=10.1016/j.jcrc.2013.10.022}}</ref>。

