=== 到院前 ===
在送達最近能夠醫治創傷的[[醫院|醫院]]前，利用{{le|穩定技巧|Stabilization (medicine)}}可以提高病患在這段路程的存活機會。[[緊急醫療服務|緊急醫療服務]]決定哪些病患需要在{{le|創傷中心|Trauma center}}接受治療，並檢查與處理{{le|ABC (medicine)||呼吸道、呼吸、循環}}、評估[[失能|失能]]、檢查其他傷害，以提供病患初步的穩定<ref name="ATLS2008">{{cite book|first=American College of Surgeons|last=Committee on Trauma|title=ATLS: Advanced Trauma Life Support Program for Doctors|publisher=American College of Surgeons|location=Chicago|edition=8th|year=2008|isbn=978-1880696316}}</ref>。

到院前以{{le|頸圈|Cervical collar}}固定[[頸部|頸部]]並將病患放在{{le|長背板|Spinal board}}上做{{le|脊椎固定|Spinal immobilization}}非常重要，但是由於缺乏支持的證據，這種做法不受歡迎；相對的，如果滿足更多特定條件，比如年齡或{{Le|神經功能缺損|Neurological deficit}}，則建議必須使用這些輔助工具<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Sundstrøm|first1=Terje|last2=Asbjørnsen|first2=Helge|last3=Habiba|first3=Samer|last4=Sunde|first4=Geir Arne|last5=Wester|first5=Knut|date=2013-08-20|title=Prehospital Use of Cervical Collars in Trauma Patients: A Critical Review|journal=Journal of Neurotrauma|volume=31|issue=6|pages=531–40|doi=10.1089/neu.2013.3094|issn=0897-7151|pmc=3949434|pmid=23962031}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Singletary|first1=Eunice M.|last2=Charlton|first2=Nathan P.|last3=Epstein|first3=Jonathan L.|last4=Ferguson|first4=Jeffrey D.|last5=Jensen|first5=Jan L.|last6=MacPherson|first6=Andrew I.|last7=Pellegrino|first7=Jeffrey L.|last8=Smith|first8=William “Will” R.|last9=Swain|first9=Janel M.|date=2015-11-03|title=Part 15: First Aid|journal=Circulation|language=en|volume=132|issue=18 suppl 2|pages=S574–89|doi=10.1161/CIR.0000000000000269|issn=0009-7322|pmid=26473003}}</ref>。移動病患前可以利用其他醫療運輸設備來幫忙，例如{{le|長軀幹固定器|Kendrick Extrication Device}}<ref>{{cite web |title=裝備櫥窗 |url=http://enews.nfa.gov.tw/one-news.asp?NewsNo=4108 |website=內政部消防署消防電子報資料庫 |accessdate=2020-09-23 |archive-date=2021-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416195407/http://enews.nfa.gov.tw/one-news.asp?NewsNo=4108 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Karbi1988">{{cite journal|first1=OA|last1=Karbi|first2=DA|last2=Caspari|first3=CH|last3=Tator|title=Extrication, immobilization and radiologic investigation of patients with cervical spine injuries|journal={{le|Canadian Medical Association Journal}}|volume=139|issue=7|pages=617–21|year=1988|pmc=1268249|pmid=3046734}}</ref>。重要的是在[[傷口|傷口]]上直接加壓以迅速控制嚴重的[[出血|出血]]，如果症狀持續，可以考慮使用{{le|止血劑|Antihemorrhagic}}或[[止血帶|止血帶]]<ref name="Moore2013p154">Moore 2013, pp. 154–66</ref>。其他狀況包括急性{{le|呼吸道阻塞|Airway obstruction}}、惡化的頸部[[血腫|血腫]]、[[意識不清|意識不清]]需要[[氣管插管|氣管插管]]等，然而目前尚不確定這些情況是在到達醫院前或在醫院中進行何者為佳<ref name="Bulger2007">{{cite journal|last=Bulger|first=EM|author2=Maier, RV|title=Prehospital care of the injured: what's new.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_surgical-clinics-of-north-america_2007-02_87_1/page/37|journal=The Surgical Clinics of North America|date=Feb 2007|volume=87|issue=1|pages=37–53, vi|pmid=17127122|doi=10.1016/j.suc.2006.09.009}}</ref>。

快速運送重傷病患可改善創傷的[[預後|預後]]<ref name="ER2008">{{cite journal|last1=Bonatti|first1=H|last2=Calland|first2=JF|title=Trauma|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_emergency-medicine-clinics-of-north-america_2008-08_26_3/page/625|journal=Emergency Medicine Clinics of North America|volume=26|issue=3|pages=625–48|year=2008|pmid=18655938|doi=10.1016/j.emc.2008.05.001}}</ref><ref name="ATLS2008" />。與地面運輸相比，[[直升機|直升機]]運輸可降低成年創傷病患的[[死亡率|死亡率]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Sullivent|first=EE|author2=Faul, M|author3=Wald, MM|title=Reduced mortality in injured adults transported by helicopter emergency medical services|journal=Prehospital Emergency Care|date=Jul–Sep 2011|volume=15|issue=3|pages=295–302|pmid=21524205|doi=10.3109/10903127.2011.569849|url=https://zenodo.org/record/1235833|access-date=2020-09-22|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009085001/https://zenodo.org/record/1235833|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在到達醫院之前，與{{le|基本救命術|Basic life support}}相比，提供{{le|進階生命救命術|Advanced life support}}並不能大幅改善重大創傷的結果<ref name="Stiell2008">{{cite journal |vauthors=Stiell IG, Nesbitt LP, Pickett W, et al |title=The OPALS Major Trauma Study: impact of advanced life-support on survival and morbidity|journal=CMAJ|volume=178|issue=9|pages=1141–52|year=2008|pmid=18427089|pmc=2292763|doi=10.1503/cmaj.071154}}</ref><ref name="Liberman2007">{{cite journal|vauthors=Liberman M, Roudsari BS |title=Prehospital trauma care: what do we really know?|journal=Curr Opin Crit Care|volume=13|issue=6|pages=691–96|year=2007|pmid=17975392|doi=10.1097/MCC.0b013e3282f1e77e}}</ref>。到院前是否應給予[[靜脈注射|靜脈輸液治療]]的相關證據尚無定論，但有些證據表示這可能有害<ref name="Dretzke2004">{{cite journal|vauthors=Dretzke J, Sandercock J, Bayliss S, Burls A |title=Clinical effectiveness and cost-effectiveness of prehospital intravenous fluids in trauma patients|journal=Health Technol Assess|volume=8|issue=23|pages=iii, 1–103|year=2004|pmid=15193210|doi=10.3310/hta8230}}</ref>。與沒有創傷中心的醫院相比，有創傷中心者治療結果較佳<ref name="ER2008" />；創傷病患能直接送到創傷治療中心者，治療結果可能較佳<ref name="Nirula2010">{{cite journal|vauthors=Nirula R, Maier R, Moore E, Sperry J, Gentilello L |title=Scoop and run to the trauma center or stay and play at the local hospital: hospital transfer's effect on mortality|journal=J Trauma|volume=69|issue=3|pages=595–99; discussion 599–601|year=2010|pmid=20838131|doi=10.1097/TA.0b013e3181ee6e32}}</ref>。

=== 到院後 ===
創傷病患的治療通常需要許多醫療專業人員的協助，包括[[醫生|醫生]]、[[護理師|護理師]]、[[呼吸治療師|呼吸治療師]]、[[社會工作者|社會工作者]]。通常先進行初步調查，評估病患的呼吸道、呼吸、循環、神經系統的狀況<ref>Moore 2013, p. 160</ref>。這些步驟可能同時進行，也可能取決於其緊迫性，例如[[氣胸#張力性氣胸|張力性氣胸]]或大動脈出血。初步調查通常包括對[[頸椎|頸椎]]的評估，儘管要等到影像檢查或病情改善後才能確定排除頸椎的問題。直接威脅生命的問題獲得控制後，病患可能被送進[[手術室|手術室]]立即以[[外科手術|外科手術]]處理傷勢，或者進行二次調查，更詳細地從頭到腳全面評估<ref>Moore 2013, p. 163</ref>。

氣管插管的適應症包括呼吸道阻塞、無法保護呼吸道、[[呼吸衰竭|呼吸衰竭]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Nemeth|first=J|author2=Maghraby, N |author3=Kazim, S |title=Emergency airway management: the difficult airway.|journal=Emergency Medicine Clinics of North America|date=May 2012|volume=30|issue=2|pages=401–20, ix|pmid=22487112|doi=10.1016/j.emc.2011.12.005}}</ref>，這些適應症的例子包括頸部穿透性創傷、正在惡化的頸部血腫、失去知覺等。創傷的復甦包括控制住活動性出血，檢查[[生命徵象|生命徵象]]、執行[[心電圖|心電圖]]、建立{{le|血管通路|Vascular access}}。應進行其他測試以取得當前[[臨床化學|血液化學數據]]，例如{{le|動脈血氣體分析|Arterial blood gas test}}或{{le|血栓彈力圖|Thromboelastography}}<ref>{{cite web |title=血栓彈力圖在病人輸血管理的臨床應用 |url=http://www.labmed.org.tw/bjournal04.asp?IsAno=16&IsBno=64&IsCno=227&IsDno=623 |website=社團法人台灣醫事檢驗學會 |accessdate=2020-09-24}}</ref><ref>Moore 2013, p. 161</ref>。一般認為[[心肺復甦術|心肺復甦術]]對因創傷而[[心搏停止|心搏停止]]的病患效果不佳，但仍建議給予<ref name=AHAPart12>{{cite journal |vauthors=Vanden Hoek TL, Morrison LJ, Shuster M, Donnino M, Sinz E, Lavonas EJ, Jeejeebhoy FM, Gabrielli A |title=Part 12: cardiac arrest in special situations: 2010 American Heart Association Guidelines for Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation and Emergency Cardiovascular Care|journal=Circulation|date=2010-11-02|volume=122|issue=18 Suppl 3|pages=S829–61|pmid=20956228|doi=10.1161/CIRCULATIONAHA.110.971069}}</ref>，處理潛在病因可能會有幫助，比如[[氣胸|氣胸]]或[[心包填塞|心包填塞]]<ref name=AHAPart12/>。

某些創傷讓訓練有素的醫療人員來維持呼吸道、呼吸、循環功能可能是有益的，例如[[口腔頜面外科|頜面]]創傷<ref name="Maxillofacial">{{cite journal|vauthors=Krausz AA, El-Naaj IA, Barak M |title=Maxillofacial trauma patient: coping with the difficult airway |journal=World Journal of Emergency Surgery |volume=4 |issue= |page=21 |year=2009|pmid=19473497 |pmc=2693512 |doi=10.1186/1749-7922-4-21 }}</ref>。

=== 藥物 ===
[[傳明酸|傳明酸]]可減少因創傷而持續流血者的死亡率，對輕度到中度[[腦外傷|腦外傷]]及電腦斷層掃描顯示有[[顱內出血|顱內出血]]的病患也有幫助<ref name="CRASH2010">{{cite journal |vauthors=Shakur H, Roberts I, Bautista R, Caballero J, Coats T, Dewan Y, El-Sayed H, Gogichaishvili T |title=Effects of tranexamic acid on death, vascular occlusive events, and blood transfusion in trauma patients with significant haemorrhage (CRASH-2): a randomised, placebo-controlled trial |journal=The Lancet |volume=376 |issue=9734 |pages=23–32 |year=2010 |pmid=20554319 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(10)60835-5}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|vauthors=Cap AP, Baer DG, Orman JA, Aden J, Ryan K, Blackbourne LH |title=Tranexamic acid for trauma patients: a critical review of the literature|journal=The Journal of Trauma|date=July 2011|volume=71|issue=1 Suppl|pages=S9–14|pmid=21795884|doi=10.1097/TA.0b013e31822114af}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|date=2019-11-09|title=Effects of tranexamic acid on death, disability, vascular occlusive events and other morbidities in patients with acute traumatic brain injury (CRASH-3): a randomised, placebo-controlled trial|url=https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(19)32233-0/abstract|journal=The Lancet|language=en|volume=394|issue=10210|pages=1713–1723|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(19)32233-0|issn=0140-6736|pmid=31623894|pmc=6853170|author1=CRASH-3 trial collaborators}}</ref>，但是似乎只有在創傷後的前三個小時內使用才有益<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Napolitano|first1=LM|last2=Cohen|first2=MJ|last3=Cotton|first3=BA|last4=Schreiber|first4=MA|last5=Moore|first5=EE|title=Tranexamic acid in trauma: how should we use it?|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-trauma-and-acute-care-surgery_2013-06_74_6/page/1575|journal=The Journal of Trauma and Acute Care Surgery|date=June 2013|volume=74|issue=6|pages=1575–86|pmid=23694890|doi=10.1097/ta.0b013e318292cc54}}</ref>。對於嚴重的出血，例如[[凝血病|凝血病]]，可能適合給予{{le|重組因子VIIa|Recombinant factor VIIa}}（一種有助於凝血的[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]）<ref name="ER2008" /><ref name="COCC2010">{{cite journal|vauthors=Roppolo LP, Wigginton JG, Pepe PE |title=Intravenous fluid resuscitation for the trauma patient|journal=Curr Opin Crit Care|volume=16|issue=4|pages=283–88|year=2010|pmid=20601865|doi=10.1097/MCC.0b013e32833bf774}}</ref>，但似乎未能降低死亡率<ref>{{cite journal  |vauthors=Hauser CJ, Boffard K, Dutton R, etal |title=Results of the CONTROL trial: efficacy and safety of recombinant activated Factor VII in the management of refractory traumatic hemorrhage |journal=J Trauma |volume=69 |issue=3 |pages=489–500 |date=September 2010 |pmid=20838118 |doi=10.1097/TA.0b013e3181edf36e |url=}}</ref>，不建議用於沒有重組因子VII缺乏症病史的病患，除非是人體試驗<ref>{{cite journal|last=Simpson|first=E|author2=Lin, Y |author3=Stanworth, S |author4=Birchall, J |author5=Doree, C |author6= Hyde, C |title=Recombinant factor VIIa for the prevention and treatment of bleeding in patients without haemophilia|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews |date=Mar 14, 2012|volume=3|issue=3|page=CD005011|pmid=22419303|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD005011.pub4|hdl=10871/13808}}</ref>。

有些[[藥物|藥物]]可以與其他治療處置合併給予，以穩定遭受嚴重損害的病患<ref name="Rosen2010" />。雖然{{le|強心劑|Inotrope}}（如[[去甲基腎上腺素_(藥物)|去甲基腎上腺素]]）有時會用於創傷導致的[[血容量減少|出血性休克]]，但仍缺乏支持的證據<ref>{{cite journal|last=Senz|first=A|author2=Nunnink, L|title=Review article: inotrope and vasopressor use in the emergency department|journal=Emergency Medicine Australasia |date=Oct 2009|volume=21|issue=5|pages=342–51|pmid=19694785|doi=10.1111/j.1742-6723.2009.01210.x}}</ref>，因此截至2012年仍未列入建議<ref name=Kob2012>{{cite journal|last=Kobayashi|first=L|author2=Costantini, TW |author3=Coimbra, R |title=Hypovolemic shock resuscitation|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_surgical-clinics-of-north-america_2012-12_92_6/page/n54|journal=The Surgical Clinics of North America|date=Dec 2012|volume=92|issue=6|pages=1403–23|pmid=23153876|doi=10.1016/j.suc.2012.08.006}}</ref>。在某些情況下，適度的低血壓是被允許的<ref>{{cite web|title=Vasopressor and Inotrope Usage in Shock|url=http://www.surgicalcriticalcare.net/Guidelines/Vasopressors%20and%20Inotropes%20in%20Shock.pdf|work=Department of Surgical Education, Orlando Regional Medical Center|accessdate=4 May 2014|date=Apr 19, 2011|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127135136/http://surgicalcriticalcare.net/Guidelines/Vasopressors%20and%20Inotropes%20in%20Shock.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 外科手術 ===
是否進行[[手術|手術]]取決於損傷的程度和解剖位置。必須先能控制住出血，然後才能有妥善的修復<ref>{{cite book |author1=Andrew B., MD Peitzman |author2=Andrew B. Peitzman |author3=Michael, MD Sabom |author4=Donald M., MD Yearly |author5=Timothy C., MD Fabian |title=The trauma manual |url=https://archive.org/details/traumamanual0000unse |publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins |location=Hagerstwon, MD |year=2002 |pages= |isbn=978-0781726412 }}</ref>。{{le|損傷控制手術|Damage control surgery}}<ref>{{cite web |title=嚴重外傷病人的初始照護 |url=https://www.sem.org.tw/EJournal/Detail/120 |website=台灣急診醫學會 |accessdate=2020-09-25}}</ref>用於處理嚴重的創傷，如果未能妥善處理，可能因{{le|代謝性酸中毒|Metabolic acidosis}}、[[失溫症|失溫症]]、[[低血壓|低血壓]]等一系列過程導致[[死亡|死亡]]<ref name="ER2008" />，手術的主要原則是採用最少的步驟來挽救生命和肢體，將比較次要的步驟留待病患狀況更穩定後再執行<ref name="ER2008" />。所有創傷病患中約15%有腹部損傷，其中約25%需要進行{{le|探查性手術|Exploratory surgery}}。可預防的創傷致死大多數起因於未能發現腹腔內出血<ref name="Management of Abdominal Trauma">{{cite book |last1=Fitzgerald |first1= J.E.F. |author-link1= |last2=Larvin |first2=Mike |author-link2= |display-authors= |author-mask= |last-author-amp= |year=2009 |orig-year= |chapter= Chapter 15: Management of Abdominal Trauma |script-chapter= |trans-chapter= |editor1-last=Baker |editor1-first=Qassim |editor1-link= |editor2-last=Aldoori |editor2-first=Munther |title=Clinical Surgery: A Practical Guide |publisher=CRC Press |pages=192–204 |isbn=978-1444109627}}</ref>。
